  description: Handle withdrawal requests with multi-step process support,
});
```

#### Conversation Analysis Algorithm
```typescript
// In IntentManager.getActiveIntentByReply()
1. Extract user/channel info from message metadata
2. Get recent messages from conversation (last 20)
3. Find current user message and previous user message
4. Filter only agent responses between these messages
5. Search for intent IDs and action names in agent response data
6. Return active intent if found, null otherwise
```

